<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00034</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROHIBITING THE IMPORTATION OF WASTES, PROVIDING PENALTIES FOR VIOLATIONS THEREOF AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Intends to prohibit the importation of wastes that have not been processed to eradicate or minimize
their environmental impact and have no beneficial value to our people or our country

Provides for a fine of not less than One Million Pesos (Php1,000,000.00) and imprisonment of not less
than six (6) months.
